causal diagram

Graph

  • [pos = ]

  • (0, 0) 

g <- dagitty('dag {
    X [pos="0,1"]
    Y [pos="1,1"]
    Z [pos="2,1"]

    X -> Y -> Z 
}')

plot(g)

  • \(X\) \(Y\) parent
  • \(Y\) \(X\) child
  • direct path
  • \(X\) \(Y\), \(Z\) ancestor
  • \(Y\), \(Z\) \(X\) descentant
  • directed path( undirected path)

Example

g <- dagitty('dag {
    X [pos="0,1"]
    Y [pos="1,1"]
    Z [pos="2,1"]
    W [pos="1,0"]
    T [pos="2,2"]
    
    X -> Y -> Z -> T
    X -> W -> Y -> T
    W -> Z
}')
plot(g)

  • \(Z\) parent \(Y,\, W\)
  • \(Z\) ancestor \(X, \, W, \, Y\)
  • \(W\) child \(Y, \, Z\)
  • \(W\) descendant \(Y, \, Y, \, Z\)
dagitty::parents(g, "Z")

[1] "W" "Y"
dagitty::ancestors(g, "Z")

[1] "Z" "Y" "X" "W"
dagitty::children(g, "W")

[1] "Y" "Z"
dagitty::descendants(g, "W")

[1] "W" "Z" "T" "Y"

Chain()

  • \(X \not\!\perp\!\!\!\perp Z\)

  • \(X \perp\!\!\!\perp Z | Y\)

  • (\(X\)) (\(Y\)) , (\(Z\)) 

g <- dagitty('dag {
    X [pos="0,1"]
    Y [pos="1,1"]
    Z [pos="2,1"]

    X -> Y -> Z 
}')

plot(g)

Fork(Common cause, )

  • \(X \not\!\perp\!\!\!\perp Z\)

  • \(X \perp\!\!\!\perp Z | Y\)

  • (\(Y\)) \(X\), \(Y\) 

g <- dagitty('dag {
    X [pos="0,1"]
    Y [pos="1,0"]
    Z [pos="2,1"]

    Y -> X 
    Y -> Z
}')

plot(g)

Collider(or immorality, )

g <- dagitty('dag {
    X [pos="0,0"]
    Y [pos="1,1"]
    Z [pos="2,0"]

    X -> Y 
    Z -> Y
}')

plot(g)

  • \(X \perp\!\!\!\perp Z\)

  • \(X \not\!\perp\!\!\!\perp Z | Y\)

  • (\(X\)) (\(Z\)) (\(Y\))

bfi <- janitor::clean_names(bfi)

bfiNoNA <- na.omit(bfi)

bfiNoNA <- bfiNoNA %>% 
    mutate(gender = factor(gender, levels = c(1, 2), labels = c("Male", "Female"))) %>%
    mutate_if(is.integer, as.numeric)
# bfiNoNA %>% str()

bfisub <- bfiNoNA %>% 
    select(age, education, c5, o1, n5)

Whitelist <- matrix(c("age", "education"),, 2, byrow = T)

colnames(Whitelist) <- c("from", "to")

Blacklist <- matrix(c("education", "age", 
                      "c5", "age", 
                      "o1", "age", 
                      "n5", "age"), , 2, byrow = T)
colnames(Blacklist) <- c("from", "to")
Blacklist

     from        to   
[1,] "education" "age"
[2,] "c5"        "age"
[3,] "o1"        "age"
[4,] "n5"        "age"

res <- bnlearn::iamb(bfisub, whitelist = Whitelist, blacklist = Blacklist)

boostrapping

boot <- boot.strength(bfisub, R = 1000, algorithm = "iamb", 
                      algorithm.args = list(whitelist = Whitelist, 
                                            blacklist = Blacklist))

qgraph(boot, nodeNames = labels, legend.cex = 0.5, edge.labels = T, layout = g$layout,
       asize = 5, edge.color = "black")
